{"tid":2095704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個炒車/fact check 經歷","createTime":"2020-07-05T16:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:44:54.000Z","uid":21730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"23cfdc63365b5eab8de8ea0aaa800e03dc2a1b9b","tid":2095704,"uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"之前謠傳義士老豆老母篤灰傳得沸沸揚揚，之後集體炒車 <br />\n仲有好多藍絲趁機抽水 <br />\n其實FC 係重要，但到底點拿掐FC？<br />\n要Check到點？<br />\n其實都好難掌握 <br />\n以下講下小小愚見，屌得細力啲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如，你一手睇到啲事，或者親身經歷嘅 <br />\n呢隻一手料難FC ，亦未必咁大需要FC ，就咁講一手料就得 <br />\n但轉發呢類資訊果陣記得寫明係二手三手EVEN N手料  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲完全FC唔到嘅野，好似報紙嘅消息人士指XXXXX<br />\n或者係匿名報料 <br />\n你永遠唔會知係邊個，無法係身分上確認事情真偽 <br />\n只能盡力求證件事先，可以的話最好唔好轉發直至你求證到件事  <br />\n<br />\n轉發之前老土都要講句，停一停諗一諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有果啲咩Facebook 會刪你post，唔俾人post <br />\n所以要手動轉果啲，都可以自己親身實驗左先（反正又無成本） <br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係從人地角度出發，去考慮你啲消息可唔可信 <br />\n令人可信嘅，從來都唔應該只係Fact check 呢2隻字  <br />\n<br />\n講完經，分享下我覺得運動以黎最on9嘅炒車經歷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係大肚婆&gt;無大肚&gt;最後原來都係有大肚單野 <br />\n首先人地果下點都無流產先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，然後醫管局「澄清」左全世界以為自己炒車，點知最後本人出黎真「澄清」 <br />\n不過醫管局都on9，明明你無問人地有無大肚，咁老定人地一定無大肚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70acc91e06014d3cd41704626bbc7ef2a5e77d2e","tid":2095704,"uid":66742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"如果果陣無瘋傳，可能醫管局都唔會炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59310441cc2a36ae7f53e4744262d28596372a0e","tid":2095704,"uid":318129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"如果係呢種呢？<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bs4hULh9Rbc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbs4hULh9Rbc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7f7ea050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bs4hULh9Rbc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096fe1c49a37eacf8be55298e1e0e7b85d85a9d8","tid":2095704,"uid":97385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"見到啲人一手料都寫fc,真係好想知佢點fc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一手料到左你度,你做fc無問題嘅都, <br />\n但係去左你度明明已經變左二手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481ba8001b672b28e317469659d888233f2fc8d6","tid":2095704,"uid":66742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:31:00.000Z","msg":"我反而好深印象初期啲捉鬼炒車，大隻啲又係鬼，有手帶又鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e119dd64209209227ba4624a24057c15d8a03fd6","tid":2095704,"uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59310441cc2a36ae7f53e4744262d28596372a0e","tid":2095704,"uid":318129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"如果係呢種呢？<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bs4hULh9Rbc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbs4hULh9Rbc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7f7ea050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bs4hULh9Rbc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"有咩要求證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求證佢地係咪一家人? <br />\n定求證個女係咪fresh grad?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gi